# Shared Packages Conventions

## Package Map

| Package | Path | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `@delivio/api` | `packages/api/` | HTTP client + WebSocket client for all frontends |
| `@delivio/types` | `packages/types/` | Shared TypeScript type definitions |
| `@delivio/ui` | `packages/ui/` | Shared React UI components (shadcn/ui based) |

## @delivio/api

- **HTTP client:** wraps `fetch` with base URL, cookie forwarding, and error handling.
- **WS client** (`packages/api/src/ws.ts`): `createWSClient(url)` returns `{ connect, disconnect, subscribe, send, isConnected }`.
  - Reconnection: exponential backoff capped at 30s.
  - Heartbeat: ping every ~25s.
  - Event dispatch: handlers registered via `subscribe(eventType, handler)`.

When adding new API endpoints, add corresponding client methods here so all frontends use the same client.

- **Shops namespace:** `api.shops.list()`, `.get()`, `.create()`, `.update()`, `.delete()`, `.listUsers()`, `.assignUser()`, `.removeUser()`.
- **Catalog methods** accept optional `shopId` parameter (passed as `x-shop-id` header).
- **Vendor settings** accept optional `shopId` for shop-scoped settings.
- **Public methods:** `api.public.shops(ref, lat?, lon?)` (filters by geofence when lat/lon provided), `.shopDetail(ref, shopId)`, `.shopProducts(ref, shopId)`, `.shopCategories(ref, shopId)`, `.shopDeliveryCheck(ref, shopId, lat, lon)`, `.geocode(address)`, `.reverseGeocode(lat, lon)`.
- **Rider geofence:** `api.riderGeofence.get()`, `.save(geofence)` — `GET/PUT /api/rider/geofence`.
- **Superadmin:** `api.superadmin.auth.login/logout/session`, `.workspaces.list/create/update`, `.users.list/create/update/delete`, `.shops.list/create/update`, `.customers.list`, `.orders.list`, `.stats()`.

## @delivio/types

- Canonical source for shared TypeScript interfaces and enums.
- **Multi-shop types:** `Shop`, `UserShop` interfaces. `Order`, `Product`, `Category`, `CartSession`, `VendorSettings` all include optional `shopId`.
- **Geofence types:** `GeoPolygon` (GeoJSON Polygon), `RiderGeofence`. `Shop` includes optional `deliveryGeofence`.
- **Superadmin type:** `Superadmin` interface (id, email, name, timestamps).
- **WSEvent** union type defines all WebSocket event payloads:
  - `OrderStatusChanged`, `OrderRejected`, `OrderDelayed`
  - `DeliveryLocationUpdate`, `DeliveryRiderArrived`, `DeliveryRequest`
  - `ChatMessage`, `ChatRead`, `ChatTyping`
- When adding a new WS event type, update the union here first, then implement server-side broadcast and client-side handler.

## @delivio/ui

- Built on **shadcn/ui** + **Tailwind CSS** + **Lucide icons**.
- Exports reusable components consumed by `apps/customer` and `apps/rider`.
- When creating a new UI component that will be used by multiple apps, add it here.
- Keep components accessible (keyboard nav, ARIA, focus management).

## Dependency Rules

- Packages must **not** depend on app-level code.
- Apps import packages via workspace references (`"@delivio/api": "workspace:*"`).
- Build order is enforced by Turborepo `dependsOn: ["^build"]`.
